      <title>纽约时报民意调查显示哈里斯和特朗普在密歇根州和威斯康星州的得票率不相上下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/harris-trump-neck-and-neck-in-nyt-polls-on-michigan-wisconsin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据《纽约时报》和锡耶纳学院周六公布的民意调查显示，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯和前总统唐纳德·特朗普在密歇根州和威斯康星州这两个摇摆州的支持率基本持平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/harris-trump-neck-and-neck-in-nyt-polls-on-michigan-wisconsin</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 10:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
