      <title>斯塔默的摇摆不定给失败的保守党带来了一线希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/starmer-s-wobbles-have-given-vanquished-tories-a-glimmer-of-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[7 月 5 日凌晨，基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，保守党总部的官员们则为退出英国政坛做好了准备，他们认为保守党的失败具有毁灭性，足以让其在一代人的时间里无法执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/starmer-s-wobbles-have-given-vanquished-tories-a-glimmer-of-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
